nawards/\">2008 Alumni Award of Merit winners: John Dunning Boice, Jr., SM '74, SD '77</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-vbdr.-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-vbdr._5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.vbdr.org\">\"VBDR.org: Veterans' Advisory Board on Dose Reconstruction, Veterans' Dose Reconstruction Program\"</a>. vbdr.org<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">5 June</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=VBDR.org%3A+Veterans%27+Advisory+Board+on+Dose+Reconstruction%2C+Veterans%27+Dose+Reconstruction+Program&amp;rft.pub=vbdr.org&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vbdr.org&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJohn+D.+Boice+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-hps-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-hps_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hps.org/aboutthesociety/people/landauer.html\">\"R.S. Landauer, Sr., Lecture Series\"</a>. hps.org<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">5 June</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=R.S.+Landauer%2C+Sr.%2C+Lecture+Series&amp;rft.pub=hps.org&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fhps.org%2Faboutthesociety%2Fpeople%2Flandauer.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJohn+D.+Boice+Jr.\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">John